text: Ace High (, literally translated as "The Four of the Hail Mary") is a 1968 Italian western movie directed by Giuseppe Colizzi and starring Eli Wallach, Bud Spencer, Terence Hill, Brock Peters, Kevin McCarthy, Bruno Corazzari, Rick Boyd. It was distributed by Paramount Pictures and is the second part of the Italian western trilogy. ==Other websites== * * Category:1968 movies Category:1960s Western (genre) movies Category:Italian Western (genre) movies Category:Paramount Pictures movies Category:Movies directed by Giuseppe Colizzi Category:Movies set in Texas Category:Movies set in Mexico
